Package subscription

Class Meal

java.lang.Object
subscription.Meal
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Meal>
public class Meal extends Object implements Comparable<Meal>
A Meal is read from the input file and has a name of the meal type and changeable balance of available meals of the particular meal type.

Meal implements Comparable interface with overridden compareTo(Meal m) to allow for lexicographic sorting if meals are stored in the sorted linked list.

Balance of particular meal type can be changed with setMealBalance method which is called in the MainProgram class when subscribing or unsubscribing to meals.
